text:
Patryce's cozy home was so fabulous! We had a wonderful stay in Austin. Patryce was unbelievably kind and accommodating. The house itself is beautiful, clean ( spotless), comfortable and in a great location. It felt like a little zen sanctuary!!! She even put beautiful books and flowers for us to enjoy.
I highly highly recommend Patryce's bungalow of coziness and relaxation!!
title: South Austin 1952 Home
